 fixed my bug and the\n\nCurrentItem.Published.ToLongDateString()', 'DateTime, ToString(), and CurrentCulture', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '35-revision-5', '', '', '2010-03-31 14:19:50', '2010-03-31 13:19:50', '', 35, 'http://www.jonathansewell.co.uk/index.php/2010/03/31/35-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
